1
00:01:22,160 --> 00:01:24,039
How is it? Does it still hurt?

2
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:28,280
Su Xia, I won't thank you.

3
00:01:28,520 --> 00:01:29,960
Whatever Han Qi does to me,

4
00:01:29,960 --> 00:01:30,920
that's my business.

5
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:32,520
It has nothing to do with you.

6
00:01:32,880 --> 00:01:33,840
And Lu Fan.

7
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:35,600
Listen.

8
00:01:36,240 --> 00:01:38,200
I will definitely marry Lu Fan.

9
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:41,620
Congratulations.

10
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:43,280
Su Xia.

11
00:01:43,880 --> 00:01:45,680
Even if you tell

12
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:47,410
Lu Fan everything about today,

13
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:49,479
he won't believe a word you say.

14
00:01:51,039 --> 00:01:53,120
You are nothing to him.

15
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,080
He hates you.

16
00:01:55,479 --> 00:01:56,880
We all hate you.

17
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:02,000
I know.

18
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:03,920
But

19
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:07,180
he should be here soon.

20
00:02:09,720 --> 00:02:10,440
Who?

21
00:02:12,320 --> 00:02:13,440
Lu Fan, of course.

22
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,220
I will kill you.

23
00:02:20,880 --> 00:02:21,720
Su Xia.

24
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:28,210
I'm telling you.

25
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:29,480
My name is Su Xia,

26
00:02:29,720 --> 00:02:31,050
and my brother is Lu Fan.

27
00:02:31,200 --> 00:02:32,460
Jian Xi can't help you.

28
00:02:32,600 --> 00:02:34,360
My brother won't let you go.

29
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:37,079
Su Xia.

30
00:02:38,880 --> 00:02:39,800
Lunatic.

31
00:02:44,720 --> 00:02:45,440
Brother.

32
00:02:49,040 --> 00:02:49,800
Su Xia.

33
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:52,720
Fan.

34
00:02:53,079 --> 00:02:53,940
What happened?

35
00:02:55,760 --> 00:02:56,560
I...

36
00:02:58,480 --> 00:02:59,280
Say it.

37
00:03:02,440 --> 00:03:03,440
It was Han Qi.

38
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:06,840
Han Qi kidnapped Jian Xi

39
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:08,720
to threaten you.

40
00:03:09,160 --> 00:03:09,840
Brother,

41
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:13,440
I just saved your fiancée.

42
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:19,360
Jian Xi,

43
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:22,480
now you can say thank you, right?

44
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:25,960
Thank you.

45
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:31,360
Han Qi?

46
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:32,720
Lu Fan.

47
00:03:33,040 --> 00:03:35,040
Now that you won't leave me a way out,

48
00:03:35,079 --> 00:03:37,010
then let's be destroyed together.

49
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:42,520
Mr. Lu,

50
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:43,840
the test results are out.

51
00:04:43,840 --> 00:04:45,440
Miss Su only has some abrasions

52
00:04:45,440 --> 00:04:46,480
and soft tissue contusions.

53
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:48,740
She can go back after resting for a while.

54
00:04:50,400 --> 00:04:51,320
Did you check everything?

55
00:04:51,320 --> 00:04:52,240
According to your request,

56
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:53,520
we did a comprehensive check,

57
00:04:53,520 --> 00:04:54,840
and found no problems.

58
00:04:55,200 --> 00:04:57,480
Miss Su just has
an old wound on her wrist,

59
00:04:58,520 --> 00:05:00,250
but it wasn't caused this time.

60
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:08,450
I'll leave first if there's nothing else.

61
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:09,560
Okay. Thank you.

62
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:22,810
What did the doctor say?

63
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:25,160
Did he say everything is fine?

64
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,720
Let's go home first.

65
00:05:27,880 --> 00:05:28,560
Su Xia.

66
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:31,200
Last night,

67
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:34,450
did you lure me into
saving you on purpose?

68
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:44,320
What about today?

69
00:05:47,159 --> 00:05:48,690
What do you think, Brother?

70
00:05:58,040 --> 00:05:58,840
Answer me.

71
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:02,040
Which one is the real you?

72
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:03,960
You know what?

73
00:06:03,960 --> 00:06:05,240
When you ask so,

74
00:06:05,280 --> 00:06:06,160
it means

75
00:06:06,280 --> 00:06:08,410
you've already been curious about me.

76
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:55,000
You're still awake this late.

77
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,730
I am waiting for you.

78
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:05,520
If I didn't go,

79
00:07:05,880 --> 00:07:06,880
what would you do?

80
00:07:09,840 --> 00:07:11,700
I would let the blood keep flowing

81
00:07:11,760 --> 00:07:12,800
until it ran dry,

82
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:14,770
or until you came to save me.

83
00:07:14,880 --> 00:07:15,920
Have you noticed

84
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:17,890
that I bet everything I have

85
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:19,440
in this gamble?

86
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:23,160
Why?

87
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:24,960
Don't tell me

88
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:27,000
you wanted me to save you.

89
00:07:29,280 --> 00:07:32,200
But I only wanted you to save me.

90
00:07:33,200 --> 00:07:36,600
I only sent that message to you.

91
00:07:38,520 --> 00:07:39,240
Why?

92
00:07:48,280 --> 00:07:49,210
All these years,

93
00:07:50,280 --> 00:07:51,409
where have you been?

94
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:53,680
Brother.

95
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:56,560
When you get curious about someone,

96
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:59,640
it means you are not far from losing.

97
00:08:05,640 --> 00:08:06,360
Answer me.

98
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:11,080
Are you sure you came to me

99
00:08:11,080 --> 00:08:12,440
just for this?

100
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:18,020
What's your relationship

101
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:19,960
with Xiao Qi?

102
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:21,460
We're friends.

103
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:24,780
What kind of friends? Boyfriend?

104
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:30,480
What if I say no?

105
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:38,559
Go to sleep.

106
00:08:51,560 --> 00:08:52,560
Damn it.

107
00:08:55,160 --> 00:08:57,040
Lu Fan didn't come back last night again?

108
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:58,970
Who is he intentionally avoiding,

109
00:08:59,800 --> 00:09:01,840
you, or Xia?

110
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:04,650
He is probably avoiding me.

111
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:07,120
Xia.

112
00:09:08,280 --> 00:09:10,540
What happened back then has long passed.

113
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:12,800
I believe Lu Fan

114
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:14,730
has also forgotten it long ago.

115
00:09:15,560 --> 00:09:18,360
Maybe it's not about what you mentioned.

116
00:09:18,800 --> 00:09:20,080
For example,

117
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:20,800
I also...

118
00:09:20,800 --> 00:09:21,520
Zhen'an,

119
00:09:21,760 --> 00:09:22,680
don't be angry.

120
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:26,040
Fan is grown up and has his own life.

121
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:28,560
Maybe he really has work to do.

122
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,240
Besides,

123
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:33,020
we are doing quite well like this now.

124
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:35,730
I stopped caring about
my status ages ago.

125
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:39,280
I believe Xia

126
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:42,760
must also see you as family.

127
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:43,960
No.

128
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:45,720
Since we are family,

129
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:47,840
I won't allow you to suffer

130
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:49,240
any grievances at home.

131
00:09:51,160 --> 00:09:52,800
Have Aunt Liang call him.

132
00:09:52,920 --> 00:09:54,760
Tell him he must come back tonight.

133
00:09:54,760 --> 00:09:56,240
Or,

134
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,900
he won't ever come back again.

135
00:10:00,520 --> 00:10:01,920
You've been abroad

136
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:04,320
for half a month.

137
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:06,220
Fan, you're working too hard.

138
00:10:06,400 --> 00:10:07,200
But it's fine.

139
00:10:08,040 --> 00:10:08,920
As soon as you came back,

140
00:10:08,920 --> 00:10:10,960
I'm the one who picked
you up at the airport.

141
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:12,690
I'm the one who truly loves you.

142
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:21,170
What are you looking at?

143
00:10:25,920 --> 00:10:26,800
Xiao Qi?

144
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:33,360
A blind date at a barbecue stand?

145
00:10:34,160 --> 00:10:36,440
Xiao Qi is quite down-to-earth.

146
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:39,800
Not bad.

147
00:10:43,520 --> 00:10:44,520
I have to say, Fan,

148
00:10:44,560 --> 00:10:45,720
the more I look at the candidate
of your sister's husband,

149
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:47,120
the more I like him.

150
00:10:48,560 --> 00:10:49,560
He's really nice.

151
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,930
Is there something wrong with you?

152
00:11:01,160 --> 00:11:03,560
I remember your high school
is right ahead.

153
00:11:04,760 --> 00:11:06,290
What a pity it was torn down.

154
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:08,810
Further ahead is the Lu family.

155
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:12,440
What a pity it's still there.

156
00:11:16,040 --> 00:11:17,570
She is the sister of a bitch.

157
00:11:17,640 --> 00:11:19,640
Don't pretend to be Mr. Lu's sister.

158
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:22,000
Come on, cut her hair.

159
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:27,330
Pull her hands apart! Pull them apart!

160
00:11:32,760 --> 00:11:33,820
What are you doing?

161
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:41,160
Are you okay?

162
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:04,560
Around here,

163
00:12:04,640 --> 00:12:06,360
it's full of the hustle
and bustle of life.

164
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:08,040
But when it is too strong,

165
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:10,180
it's easy for people to indulge in it.

166
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:12,760
Your words

167
00:12:13,640 --> 00:12:15,120
show you're still sober.

168
00:12:15,720 --> 00:12:16,480
Then,

169
00:12:17,520 --> 00:12:18,360
do me a favor.
